## Training Schedule (3-Month Plan)

### Week 1-4: Foundation
- **Daily:** 30 min tactical puzzles
- **Mon/Wed/Fri:** 1 hour opening study (focus: fixing critical lines)
- **Tue/Thu:** 1 hour calculation training
- **Weekend:** 2 hours - play slow games (30+0 or longer)
- **Sunday:** 2 hours - analyze all games from week

### Week 5-8: Intensify
- **Daily:** 45 min tactical puzzles (harder)
- **Mon/Wed/Fri:** 1 hour endgame study
- **Tue/Thu:** 1 hour opening repertoire building
- **Weekend:** Play 2-3 tournament games
- **Sunday:** Deep analysis session

### Week 9-12: Tournament Prep
- **Daily:** Tactics + Opening review
- **Mon-Fri:** Play 1 long game daily (analyze after)
- **Weekend:** Simulated tournament conditions
- **Focus:** Implementing all improvements in real games

